General Information

Swisse Ultiboost Memory + Focus is a premium quality formula containing ginkgo, brahmi and B vitamins, to help support brain function, healthy mental performance and provide support during times of stress.

Memory Function: Brahmi is included to support memory function and recall.

Mental Performance: Vitamin B5 helps support healthy mental performance. Ginkgo helps maintain healthy circulation and the delivery of oxygenated blood to the brain.

Support During Stress: The body may have an increased need for B group vitamins during periods of nervous tension and stress. Vitamins B5 and B6 are important for the adrenals. Healthy adrenal function helps support the body's response to stress.

Energy Production: Formulated with B group vitamins to support energy production and vitality. B group vitamins contribute to a reduction in tiredness and fatigue.

Swisse Ultiboost Memory + Focus has been formulated based on scientific evidence to provide key ingredients beneficial for healthy brain function in a convenient dose.

Size: 50 Pack

Warnings

If symptoms persist consult your healthcare practitioner. Vitamin supplements should not replace a balanced diet. Do not take while on warfarin therapy without medical advice.

Ingredients

EACH TABLET CONTAINS:

VITAMIN B1 (thiamine hydrochloride) 25 mg

VITAMIN B2 (riboflavin) 35 mg

NICOTINAMIDE 20 mg

VITAMIN B5 (pantothenic acid from calcium pantothenate 70 mg) 64.13 mg

VITAMIN B6 (pyridoxine from pyridoxine hydrochloride 25 mg) 20.56 mg

VITAMIN B12 (cyanocobalamin) 25 mcg

STANDARDISED EXTRACTS EQUIVALENT TO DRY:

BRAHMI (Bacopa monnieri) whole plant (equiv. bacosides calculated as bacoside A 84 mg) 3.73 g

GINKGO (Ginkgo biloba) leaf (equiv. ginkgo flavonglycosides 14.4 mg, ginkgolides & bilobalide 3.6 mg) 3 g

Directions

ADULT DOSAGE: One tablet twice daily, during or immediately after a meal, or as directed by a healthcare professional.
TEENAGE DOSAGE: (Mental Performance, Energy Production, Support During Stress): One tablet daily.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 30 degrees Celsius. Do not use if cap seal is broken.
